The AI Resume Ranking & Job Portal is a web-based application designed to simplify the recruitment process by automatically analyzing and ranking resumes based on job requirements.
It helps recruiters shortlist candidates efficiently while allowing job seekers to apply for relevant roles through a centralized platform.

This project was developed as part of the B.Tech (KTU 2024 Scheme) curriculum under the subject Basic Concepts of Computer Networks (PBCCT 304).
# ğŸ¤– AI Resume Ranking & Job Portal ğŸš€

## ğŸ“Œ Project Overview
The **AI Resume Ranking & Job Portal** is a web-based application designed to simplify the recruitment process by automatically analyzing and ranking resumes based on job requirements.  
It helps recruiters efficiently shortlist candidates while enabling job seekers to apply for relevant roles through a centralized platform.

This project was developed as part of the **B.Tech (KTU â€“ 2024 Scheme)** curriculum under the subject  
**Basic Concepts of Computer Networks (PBCCT 304)**.

---

## ğŸ¯ Objectives
- Automate resume screening using AI-based ranking  
- Reduce manual effort in shortlisting candidates  
- Provide a simple and user-friendly job portal  
- Improve accuracy and fairness in candidate selection  

---

## ğŸ› ï¸ Features
- User registration and login (Recruiter & Job Seeker)  
- Resume upload and parsing  
- AI-based resume ranking  
- Job posting and application system  
- Dashboard for recruiters to view ranked resumes  
- Secure and efficient data handling  

---

## ğŸ§  Technologies Used
- **Frontend:** HTML, CSS, JavaScript  
- **Backend:** Python (Flask / Django)  
- **Database:** MySQL / SQLite  
- **AI / NLP:** Resume parsing, keyword matching  
- **Others:** REST APIs, basic networking concepts  

